text: Eddy Lembo (born 10 November 1980 in Miramas) is a former French-Algerian cyclist. ==Palmares== ;2001 :1st Tour du Doubs :3rd Tro Bro Leon ;2002 :1st stage 1 Tour de Suisse :3rd Tour du Finistère ;2008 :1st stage 1 Tour de Guadeloupe ;2009 :1st stage 1 Tour conseil général de Guadeloupe :1st stage 1 Tour de Marie Galante ==References== Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:French male cyclists Category:Algerian male cyclists
